descriptions.help: Displays Serium's documentation and details of each command.
descriptions.ping: Get the latency between client and API server, also this determinds how fast bot will send message.
descriptions.serverinfo: Displays current server's counts and infos like region.
descriptions.userinfo: Show infos like user ID or maybe else.
descriptions.language: Sets your default language to use Serium.
descriptions.cat: Shows you a random cat image.
descriptions.dog: Shows you a random dog image.
descriptions.welcome: Sends welcome message to new member.
descriptions.crypto: Hashes the context which you served.
descriptions.flipcoin: Flip a coin and see which is in front.
descriptions.wiki: Search things on Wikipedia and get the extract of descriptions.
descriptions.crypto: Creates hashes of context which you added to option.
descriptions.md5: Creates MD5 hashes of context which you added to option.
descriptions.say: Just like you! Talking like you.
descriptions.sayd: I am just faster then you! Deletes you wrote before sending copy of your message.
descriptions.avatar: Loads user's avatar, it is also available on userinfo too.
descriptions.itunes: Search songs on iTunes and launch iTunes in-app by clicking the link(maybe only available on iOS).
descriptions.applicationinfo: Get what version of Serium is running in this server.
